Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.89,0:20:06.39,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&FFFFFF}{\bord1.7\blur0.7\3c&1a1a1a\4c&1a1a1a}我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:06.39,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&FFFFFF}{\bord1.7\blur0.7\3c&1a1a1a\4c&1a1a1a}まあ　そうか
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.90,0:20:08.31,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&DEDEDE}{\bord1.5\blur0.7}{\3c&0D0D0D\4c&0D0D0D}那些王公贵族啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.90,0:20:08.31,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&DEDEDE}{\bord1.5\blur0.7}{\3c&0D0D0D\4c&0D0D0D}お貴族様って
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.31,0:20:11.36,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&DEDEDE}{\bord1.5\blur0.7}{\3c&0D0D0D\4c&0D0D0D}总是铁了心要护着自己的财宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.31,0:20:11.36,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&DEDEDE}{\bord1.5\blur0.7}{\3c&0D0D0D\4c&0D0D0D}あの手のお宝にやたらと固執するもんな
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.90,0:20:13.90,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur0.7\3c&333333\4c&333333}这只是一方面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.90,0:20:13.90,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur0.7\3c&333333\4c&333333}それもあるけど
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.32,0:20:15.36,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur0.7\3c&333333\4c&333333}你刚刚说转手
